Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passing the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since I was a baby,\Nthere was a shogi board in front of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I grew up in a northeastern village\Nthat had a lot of snow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were more cows and roosters\Nthan people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And of those people,\Nmost were senior citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There weren't any other children my own age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There weren't even enough kids\Nto play baseball or soccer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I grew up not playing them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For pastimes, I could catch bugs by myself,\Nplay video games, or read books.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one winter day,\Nafter I did all of those things,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a few old men from the neighborhood\Ntaught me how to play shogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the Gold General.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For video games, manga, and novels,\Nthe end always came quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But with shogi, there was never an end,\Nno matter how far I went.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It captivated me to no end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By second grade,\NI was beating the adults in the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By third grade,\NI would regularly take a bumpy bus ride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to a small shogi training hall in the city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even there, I climbed up the ranks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I lost.\N- Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This kid is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My teacher from the training hall\Nintroduced me to Mr. Ohuchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became his student\Nand joined the Tokyo association.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For a middle-schooler like me,\NTokyo was far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get funds for transportation\Nto the association twice a month,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would pick apples or peaches in the village,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}help harvest rice in the fall,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and take care of cows in the winter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kai is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe we can finally have\Na master from our village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The old men of the village truly supported me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to my hard-earned wages\Nand the encouragement of the old men{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the local shogi club members,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I continued going to the association.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While being jolted by the overnight bus...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From that time,\Nmy stomach has been like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like everyone said, the 3rd-dan league\Nwas a den of wolves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was stuck there for years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The brat who was a "genius" back home{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was just one more brat in Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tokyo-Bound Highway Bus Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, the old men of the village\Nnever stopped encouraging me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seat of the overnight bus\Nwould creak and squeak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The road at night went on forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eventually, I couldn't tell whether the creaking\Nwas the seat, my stomach, or my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would have nightmares of riding on and on,\Nbut never getting anywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I just couldn't let\Neveryone's faith in me go to waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't want to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm probably still carrying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that same pain now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay. Don't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some random things,\Nso I'll put them in your refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry for the trouble.\N- No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Maru S
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had some tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some udon noodles.\NCan I use your stove?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're easy on the stomach\Nif you make them really soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in that case,\NI might be able to eat them. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father often suffered from stomach pains,\Nso I kind of remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kouda gets stomach pains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I put an egg in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. He meant his real father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can eat this. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:06:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mr. Shimada, I'll be going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your fourth match is in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I think you should focus\Non getting better, health-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you overdo it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'll be all right.\NMy stomach is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, it never hurts during a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But that being said, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't often like to make sealed moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but during the natural flow of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sealed Move Envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a move came up in which I thought,\N"This is a good one,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shimada Souya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I made that my sealed move,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4-f-Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not 6-f-Silver, but same, Silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6-e-Pawn takes that Silver,\N5-e-Rook takes 6-e-Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that's how I'd go,\Nbut I overlooked 4-f-Bishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll have me checkmated before lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Struggle Struggle Flail Flail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was racking my brain, trying to think of\Na way I could still stick it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my stomach was going "bang bang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was writhing until morning, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did I want to say again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is why I'm telling you\Nthat you need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I see. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with a static rook.\NWould you go with a ranging rook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not listening to me at all, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being useful to you at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one here who's benefiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm C-1 and you're Rank A, so I'm learning\Na lot by playing against you, Mr. Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But am I giving you anything in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say the same things sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "It's disturbing."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um... How can I put it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's disturbing... or like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Souya saw that 3-g-Silver,\Nhe said the same thing in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That 3-g-Silver is disturbing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you two are kind of similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not anything in particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if anything, maybe I'd say it's your viewpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're both all-rounders,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and your flexibility in switching\Nbetween offense and defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the timing of your judgment\Nwhen pressed for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So when you're sitting across from me\Nand playing as you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it feels a little like I've captured the feeling\Nof a viewpoint similar to Souya's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a stopgap,\Nbut it's better than doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's Master Souya like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you have that many titles,\Nyou don't really show up at the Shogi Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe to sign certificates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He reminds me of a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Quiet, white, and gentle,\Nlike an egret or crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of those thin big birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know "The Tortoise and the Hare," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's higher than the "hare."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a hare, but a "bird."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at Souya, I feel like a tortoise\Nor a bug crawling on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not belittling myself.\NThat's just the image I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What stumps me is the hare\Nself-destructs by being overconfident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Souya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though he is someone who is labeled\Nas a "genius," he doesn't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how high he climbs,\Nhe never relaxes and is never overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't reduce the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would always just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I watched as Souya, the same age as me,\Nblew in and out of the association like a wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I watched as he became a professional\Nand quickly ascended the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But just because the distance between us\Nisn’t decreasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that’s no reason for me\Nto stop trying to progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it's obvious\Nthat I couldn't get ahead of him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is not an excuse for me to not make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should go see a doctor.\NPlease, let me take you to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine. I already go to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Mr. Shimada...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plenty of medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living with stomach pain\Nsince my teens, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of my daily life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hate it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My innards are the only thing\NI can't train to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kiriyama, could you get me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for summoning you here\Nwhen I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Will you hang out with me\Nfor a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won the right to challenge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want it to come\Nto a pathetic end, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they've still got it hanging up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at my local train station, even today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What makes it worse is I'm the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only Rank B or higher from Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From the City of Shogi, Tendou,\NLet's Get a Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I just can't let that banner\Nhang there and become stained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:27.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passing the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:31.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Nozomi 15 will be departing at 8:05.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you'd like some warm tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in the front pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take just over two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake you up when we arrive,\Nso please get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's already do-or-die{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straight losses...\NThat's the one thing I don't want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...at Mr. Shimada's insistence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I continued practicing with him,\Neven in that state.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}looking at Mr. Shimada's pale sleeping face,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I had the feeling\NI should have refused everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and make him rest more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I couldn't help but feel uneasy and regretful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Kyoto, this is Kyoto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, where's the taxi stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the right. Towards Kyoto Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- To Kyoto Hotel Number Two, please.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama. Glad you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, sorry to make you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach again?\NMan, you've always been a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do stomach transplants these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll never be able to win a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Chairman, please don't say crazy things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Get some rest\Nin your room until the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Show them to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back when it becomes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I put water, tea, and your phone\Nnext to the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything,\Nplease call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of sound like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Am I being annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get a book and something to drink\Nat a convenience store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You surprise me, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I took you for more of a cool, modern kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.95,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20th Lion King Tournament Seven Match Battle\NFourth Match in Kyoto,\NTournament Eve Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bringing Shimada here was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I've got to fetch Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably underestimating it\Nsince he lives in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He lives here, by Ginkaku-ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An incredible place like that?\NIsn't it in the middle of a tourist spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. It's really quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone else at his home\Nwho you could call?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody picks up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's living with his grandma now,\Nand she's a bit hard of hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Kyoto, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been here since the class trip\Nin middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Hina and her sisters would like it\Nif I brought back souvenirs for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. It's fine, right?\NThis is our free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So he's free to do what he wants.\N- Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.77,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate Within\N5 & 7 Turns\NHandbook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place that I especially want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the pre-match reception for the fourth game\Nof the Lion King Tournament began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada was surrounded by everyone\Nand answered their questions with a smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he hasn't really eaten since last night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he was in pain just now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this. If it keeps up until tomorrow,\Nit'll be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm painfully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The most important job\Nis showing everyone a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But another important duty is standing before\Nthe people who prepared this place for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand that. I understand, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time there was a camera flash,\NI felt a pain in my chest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had the feeling that each flash{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}caused a burning sensation\Nin Mr. Shimada's stomach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're talking to each other?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving, but quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why all of a sudden? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I believe I carried out my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to help me, and said,\N"Leave the rest to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yo! Good job working the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sorry, but I'd like to turn in early\Nto be ready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No problem, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you just slip out, no one will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Besides, everyone came here to see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So-u-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chairman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as I greet everyone, the rest\Nis pretty much always a Souya photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You've never really\Nstood out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or stood much at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman... Chairman, please, enough...\NReally, I think that's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He really does piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The way his skin is so shiny,\Nor how fluffy he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.87,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heeheehee
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.87,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I know, right?\NEven though you're the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If anything, you and Gotou\Nseem like the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I asked Smith to help you with a room,\Nso go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He's here as a substitute observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's okay. I can go to an internet café.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Idiot, you're not going to some café.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Smith is in the hall, so go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Have a good night!\N- See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even at a time like this,\Nyou're worrying about other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Things like that, no wonder his stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well this is troublesome. I was about\Nto enjoy some luxurious "me" time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'll just go to a net café! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me so seriously.\NI was kidding, so don't be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Incoming Call{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, how are things over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I was thinking about turning in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And how is it over there? Feeling lonely\Nwithout me around? No problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that right? A healthy appetite, too?\NDevoured it all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Strawberry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make that voice\Nat someone else like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:39.71,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thump-Thump-Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that his girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she's with someone else? A love triangle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it okay for me to be here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lap? On your lap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?! She hates when\NI hold her and never sits on my lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gloom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Mr. Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Fwoooo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:22:01.23,DefaultLeftM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,\Nmy kitten...\Njust,\Nouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama... I'm going out for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}S-See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as if nothing had happened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the night turned to dawn, and the curtain rose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the Lion King Tournament's fourth match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is now 9:00, so Lion King Souya,\Nplease make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada, were you able\Nto sleep some last night?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He looks grim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is his stomach still bothering him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I have done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I have refused to practice\Nand forced him to relax?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regret as I might, the curtain of battle\Nhad been cut and dropped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was too late for anyone\Nto reach their hand out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, so suddenly?\NBut it starts in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!\NI did try to contact you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.77,0:24:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would've flown there\Nif I hadn't had a match, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I even bought new formal wear, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.53,0:24:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lion King Tournament,\NMr. Shimada's battle still continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I have to go over\Nand make more udon noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.70,0:24:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion", too.
